  "description": "<p>The Vaults: Shoanti burial mounds, brick sewers, and Thassilonian deeps (Appendix 7).<strong>City tables:</strong> add Korvosa's current Danger modifier to the d% roll (+10 Unrest/Plagued · +20 Martial Law · +30 Anarchy — see the Conversion Guide's Reputation page); halve the roll to skew safer. Base rate everywhere: 20% per travel day or night of rest.</p>",
